sequenceDiagram
    participant World
    participant Controller as AGCFPlayerController
    participant Pawn as ACharacter
    participant PawnExt as UGCFPawnExtensionComponent
    participant PossessComp as UGCFControllerPossessionComponent

    World->>Pawn: Spawn Pawn
    Pawn->>PawnExt: BeginPlay
    PawnExt->>PawnExt: CheckDefaultInitialization()

    World->>Controller: Spawn Controller
    Controller->>Pawn: Possess(Pawn)

    Pawn->>PawnExt: HandleControllerChanged
    PawnExt->>PawnExt: RefreshAbilityActorInfo
    PawnExt-->>PossessComp: PawnControllerAssigned Event

    alt Controller already exists
        PossessComp->>PossessComp: Immediate Bind
    else Wait for Event
        PossessComp->>PossessComp: Wait PawnControllerAssigned
    end

    PossessComp->>Controller: SetNewPawn(Pawn)
    Controller->>Controller: Initialize Input / Camera / Movement
